	This decorative piece is carved from onyx with a polished finish for a smooth touch and is ideal to use as a kitchen utensil holder, as a desk tidy for pens and such like or as decorative storage for dried flowers. This decorative onyx piece would make the perfect gift idea for someone who is a lover of natural stone items or anyone who loves to fill their houses with pretty and decorative accessories. This gorgeous onyx desk tidy measures 12.5cm tall and 10cm in diameter. Onyx forms in parallel bands with a variety of colours mainly greens and browns, and it is often used for carving. Please note that as onyx is a naturally formed product each piece may vary slightly in colour and pattern from the picture shown.</p>
